    "text": "Elderly Care Tax Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exempt recipients of home care services under federally-assisted state or local government home care programs for the elderly or disabled from payment of employment taxes for amounts paid to service providers. Imposes liability for payment of such taxes on the fiscal administrators of such programs."
